**# CHECK FOR THE ELEMENT WHICH IS GREATER THAN FROM IT'S RIGHT AND LEFT BOTH. (NUMS[I-1]<NUMS[I] && NUMS[I]>NUMS[I+1])
# IF THIS CONDITION IS CORRECT CHECK ALL ITS LEFT TILL THEY FOLLOW DECREASING ORDER 
# SIMILIARLY CHECK ALL IT'S RIGHT TILL THEY FOLLOW DECREASING ORDER AS WELL.
# AFTER GETTING THE INDEX'S TILL THEY ARE FOLLOWING DECREASING ORDER FROM LEFT AND RIGHT
# (CONSIDERING BOUNDRY SHOULD NOT VOILETED) =>FIND MAX IF ANY MOUNTAIN HAS BEEN FOUND BEFORE AND NOW. ANS=MAX(ANS,RIGHT-LEFT+1)
